OL,6,GThis week marks a very special
OL,7,Gbirthday for a very special magazine.
OL,8,GThe 100th birthday of Radio Times is
OL,9,Gan occasion to celebrate.
OL,11,FRT today is a premium product ` and
OL,12,Fpriced accordingly. It is the only TV
OL,13,Flistings magazine aimed at selective
OL,14,Fviewers and the only one which
OL,15,Fregularly covers serious programmes
OL,16,Fand issues about broadcasting itself.
OL,18,FBut during its years as the BBC's own
OL,19,Flistings magazine, it's character
OL,20,Fclosely reflected that of BBC TV and
OL,21,Fradio.
