OL,6,FBut of course RT in the old days had
OL,7,Flinks to Presentation and even
OL,8,Foccasionally covered Pres.
OL,10,FThe "adverts" for the magazine up
OL,11,Funtil around 1990 were made by the
OL,12,FBBC Promotions team within Pres and
OL,13,Fwere often more like trailers for the
OL,14,Fprogrammes themselves.
OL,16,FPres fans of a certain vintage
OL,17,Fremember the programme menu advising
OL,18,Fthere were "full details in Radio
OL,19,FTimes" and announcers describing late
OL,20,Fchanges as a "change to the programme
OL,21,Fbilled in Radio Times".
