OL,6,FProgramme slides sometimes featured
OL,7,Fpictures taken for the magazine and
OL,8,Fannouncers grabbed their copy to
OL,9,Fcover unplanned gaps.
OL,11,FSometimes the pages of RT even tell
OL,12,Fus about changes to Pres.
OL,14,FIn October 1960, when Pres was
OL,15,Foverhauled, RT introduced the new
OL,16,Fannouncers (including Michael Aspel
OL,17,Fand Judith Chalmers) and even
OL,18,Fexplained the new format for
OL,19,Ftimechecks.
