OL,6,FFebruary 1985 saw a relaunch of BBC
OL,7,FOne. While EastEnders made the cover,
OL,8,Fon page three readers were greeted by
OL,9,Fa large picture of the new COW globe.
OL,11,FIn 1991, the new channel idents were
OL,12,Frevealed on the listings pages ` just
OL,13,Fas RT was preparing to become an all-
OL,14,Fchannel guide.
OL,16,FAnd how many other TV guides would
OL,17,Fput a BBC Two ident on the cover?
OL,18,FWell it happened in 2004.
OL,20,FRT has not been a BBC publication for
OL,21,Fmore than a decade and has covered
OL,22,Fall major channels for 32 years.
